movies.title: Rush
movies.plot: A biographical drama centered on the rivalry between Formula 1 drivers James Hunt and Niki Lauda during the 1976 Formula One motor-racing season.
movies.awards: Nominated for 2 Golden Globes. Another 6 wins & 63 nominations.
